[{"Code":"en","Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykc-mkqkq4-669\"><a id=\"_sdhiqmotzdm1\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykc-fvndco-670\"><a id=\"_bmt4n521ihwu\" display=\"false\"></a>Account Activation Flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-2r1yc5-671\">This document outlines the standard operating procedure (SOP) for Vietnam account activation, providing a clear overview of the end-to-end onboarding flow. </p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-9y75h9-672\">The flow covers each stage from request submission, underwriting review, contract signing, and activation. By following this structured process, Xendit Vietnam ensures that merchant onboarding is handled efficiently, transparently, and in accordance with regulatory and internal standards.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-dreou6-673\">The information of the activation process can be referred to this flow chart:</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-noyr45-674\"><img data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-svpgvy-675\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/kyc-flow_-vn-account-activation-image-qts5zkaj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykd-k8pc3w-676\">This table shows the detailed explanation of the flow:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:60px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-7u7du9-677\">Stage</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-pft09t-678\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-2rz4ns-679\">Description</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-ar14z3-680\">Party/PIC</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-2mzio1-681\">Request Submission</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyke-u3qjx0-682\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-jg9gfb-683\">Merchant submits onboarding requests together with required documents via Xendit website. The request arrives in Slack channel (#vietnam-pg-activation-request)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-imkt7r-684\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-9wic95-685\">Underwriting</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-uu3etn-686\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-t65hao-687\">Xendit VN Ops reviews documentation according to criteria set out corresponding Schedule (depending type of merchant)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykf-cvujhl-688\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-5abbay-689\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-35kbdw-690\">Xendit VN Ops seek consultation (if needed) from VN Legal</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-h0adwl-691\">Raise ticket in #Legal-request for review.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-awlwph-692\">Xendit VN Ops</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-wlg61q-693\">Xendit VN Legal</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-3oo588-694\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykg-8sqd5k-695\">Xendit VN Ops reaches out to merchant via email to collect sufficient documents according to corresponding Schedule and consultation of VN Legal</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-nrng0b-696\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-c6rnqm-697\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-9ie0rl-698\">Once the documents are sufficient, Xendit VN Ops send email to AppotaPay for review and approval</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-y7vsvg-699\">Xendit VN Ops</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-ke1950-700\">AP Legal</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-1nf8s8-701\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykh-jgo2di-702\">AppotaPay approves onboarding the merchant</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-qivkx4-703\">Xendit VN Ops</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-br07w7-704\">AP Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-1wa1vf-705\">Contract Signing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-lw8edi-706\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-ascf7f-707\">Xendit VN Ops choose either the Master Service Agreement or POS Acquiring Agreement in this <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1kZYkuGqZxQcV3idEKB6GRT3-xfrVadTz\"><u>folder</u></a> and send to the merchant</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-np3k6o-708\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyki-4yi1p8-709\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-uu2w26-710\">Xendit VN Ops consult VN Legal in case the merchant wishes to amend terms of the contract </p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-9z3q67-711\">Raise ticket in #Legal-request for review.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-j8jd8b-712\">Xendit VN Ops</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-qto71w-713\">Xendit VN Legal</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-y677ko-714\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-qthmle-715\">Once the contract is finalized, Xendit VN Ops procure signing from the merchant in wet-ink</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-t6qah8-716\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykj-o5gjfx-717\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-mw4k7f-718\">Once the contract is signed by the merchant, Xendit VN Ops procure signing from AppotaPay’s legal representative</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-bm0xxb-719\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-xum650-720\">Activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-ps6bci-721\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-kdost3-722\">Xendit VN Ops informs AppotaPay to activate payment channels (card/virtual accounts/e-wallet)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-1cw6uu-723\">Xendit VN Ops</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykk-b9ukpj-724\"><a id=\"_le7wrrzdv5cd\" display=\"false\"></a>Business Due Diligence</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-iqcbr8-725\">The Business Due Diligence (BDD) process guides MO Agents in verifying a merchant’s business information during onboarding. Agents review the merchant’s website, business description, and industry classification to ensure they align with Xendit’s policies and risk requirements.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-xiorak-726\">Below are the general criteria a merchant's website must meet during the verification process:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-2soo1g-727\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-bg2uvr-728\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7p-ihcx50-114\">The website or App must be ready, live, and accessible.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-kihb49-729\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7p-t48xf3-115\">The website should match the nature of the business registered with Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-tofz32-730\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7p-lkipp7-116\">The website should have information of certificate of web/app ownership</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-x6ez1z-731\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7p-npj01s-117\">The website should have payment policy, return policy, and shipping and delivery policy</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-clmt1e-732\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7p-lwvgeo-118\">The website should offer product warranty</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-dtkz4h-733\"><a id=\"_emoc9dep0n3r\" display=\"false\"></a>Legal Due Diligence</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-y0gcss-734\">The Legal Due Diligence (LDD) process enables MO Agents to verify the validity of legal documents submitted by merchants during onboarding. The documents required for Xendit Vietnam to register with Xendit vary depending on the industry type.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-658z2t-735\"><a id=\"_8nfd6ngebl2f\" display=\"false\"></a>KYC documents for Online Services</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-qon6ik-736\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-81kf19-737\">Documents</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykl-ft9xcg-738\">Details</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-raykqj-739\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-tud9bv-740\">Business License</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-rsnd7e-741\">The document must include the registered industry code</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-nylcf5-742\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-47igur-743\">Sub-licenses for certain industry</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-jikghu-744\">For more information, please refer to this docs <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1MJ49y6ct6WvQocohoPSDU3yBd3MgSY2j/edit?usp=drive_link&amp;ouid=106980730229309164285&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\"><u>List_danh_mục_ngành_nghề_KD_có_điều_kiện_15072024.docx</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykm-mn9gu0-745\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-so3yrp-746\">ID of legal representative</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-98wm2p-747\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-6830ov-748\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7q-ik3c99-119\">The ID should not be expired</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-j3v5y5-749\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7q-gtt56w-120\">The ID should show the full picture of the representative</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-28iaxe-750\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-dzk4jm-751\">ID of authorized signatory</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-wk0837-752\">Only if authorized person sign the contract</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-bv29fr-753\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykn-wjl1fy-754\">Registration for e-comm website/ app with Ministry of Industry and Trade</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-3vqbt0-121\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-txtrfr-755\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-qaolof-756\">Proof of business</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-2urwvx-757\">Documents to prove business activities, including:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-t135q2-758\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-141hsg-759\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-l1gtei-122\">Pictures of business office/headquarters</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-ik5of3-760\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-oe9n1r-123\">Tax payment documents (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-tvcx0h-761\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-hn0oqv-124\">Import invoices proving the origin of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-4v1dkp-762\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-ykszwe-125\">Warehouse images, distribution agency contracts (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-9o5421-763\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-d96qqk-126\">Sales invoices</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-xkh07e-764\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-71lims-127\">Image of the sales system recording online transactions (buyer information</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-ux6q46-765\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-gicmwi-128\">quantity of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-4rhjkz-766\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-2a4a75-129\">Value of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-32jkq0-767\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7r-7hlwz3-130\">Shipping bill corresponding to the transaction</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-2r0zxd-768\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyko-nvsrod-769\">Website/App Certificate</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-c6lpo3-770\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-vlfzka-771\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7s-c5ahyq-131\">Website registration certificate</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-hh1aho-772\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7s-pkt3ae-132\">Google Play or App Store account certificate</p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-gboe97-773\"><a id=\"_lqhrjey0ukb\" display=\"false\"></a>KYC documents for Offline Services (POS)</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-txnkc3-774\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-t79azd-775\">Documents</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-f9pzhd-776\">Details</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-rkpohw-777\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykp-ttk7cn-778\">Business License</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykq-to51h7-779\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykq-52j78a-780\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7s-0faiig-133\">List of registered industry codes</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykq-1al8yi-781\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7s-swcs7s-134\">Business location registration certificate (for merchant with multiple locations)</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykq-xs2srb-782\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykq-efsri7-783\">Sub-license for certain industry (conditional business lines)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-dazlds-784\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-pbja2b-785\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7t-5hx7kx-135\">Hotels: star ranking (if any), fire safety certificate, security certificate, food safety (if having restaurant)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-g6c3my-786\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7t-ypjdes-136\">Restaurants/Coffee: food safety certificate</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-pvdu84-787\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-lrabf7-788\">ID of legal representative</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-okl3hf-789\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-oera09-790\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7t-i469xq-137\">The ID should not be expired</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-snja9j-791\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7t-57m5v2-138\">The ID should show the full picture of the representative</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-mm7ctn-792\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykr-5abpmz-793\">ID of authorized signatory</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-dm1lvl-794\">Only if authorized person sign the contract</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-8j9x55-795\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-i5fbwc-796\">Authorization letter</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-z7cqda-797\">Document that is signed by legal representative to appoint the authorized person</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-oti6f1-798\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-uwq87a-799\">Proof of business</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-6tjh47-800\">Image to verify business location applied for the POS/EDC (minimum 05 (five) images), including:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-6tjwb5-801\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyks-70zf89-802\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7u-pw2unt-139\">The photo of the exterior facade contains the business address (house number, street, ward, district, city...) that matches the registered address on the Business License.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-1ve43p-803\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7u-b6f8kn-140\">In case the address of the merchant is in a building, it is necessary to take a clear photo of the building with the building name.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-d58gg1-804\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7u-mkmg11-141\">Photos inside the store, the business area of ​​the merchant (for example: cashier desk area, goods/service display area...)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-pftyz7-805\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7u-8pvct4-142\">Product images (in case the merchant selling software, ticketing and services does not have a clear product image, the merchant provides the following information: office photo, website, fanpage, cooperation contract, etc., invoice clearly shows the products and services)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-rtnpkn-806\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7u-i1y2z3-143\">In case of multiple branches, need to provide image of all branches</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-1gqb30-807\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-ewm1cs-808\">Additional proof of business</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-ceu4fb-809\">Documents proving the origin of products and goods: import invoices, warehouse images, distribution agency contracts… (if any)</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-n0n778-810\"><a id=\"_y93x7ol9ena\" display=\"false\"></a>KYC documents for Foreign Online Services</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-7qjqjo-811\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-ii3ssy-812\">Documents</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykt-cc4a5z-813\">Details</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-rormex-814\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-8k4mk8-815\">Business License</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-he5o2b-816\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-vxnt5p-817\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7v-5e8h53-144\">Business file</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-hocmse-818\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7v-w94dzs-145\">Certificate of incorporation</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-2c69qs-819\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-0e0f62-820\">Sub-license for specific industry (if applicable)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-jx5fk9-821\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-zeszj5-822\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7v-9hu668-146\">Only for the Payment service providers/money service operators/remittance Merchants (Reseller/remittance merchant): require PAYMENT SERVICE PROVIDERS/MONEY SERVICE OPERATORS/REMITTANCE LICENSE</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyku-y1vill-823\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-9scs0d-824\">Passport of legal representative</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-ljgak1-825\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-fn377u-826\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7w-mexuki-147\">The passport should not be expired</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-id3a82-827\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7w-sxp3c7-148\">The passport should show the full picture of the representative</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-m3mrhe-828\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-p5oyib-829\">Beneficial and owner information</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-iu4vv4-830\">Individuals and organizations owning more than 25% of capital or shares in the company</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-tu4jn0-831\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykv-fc7wth-832\">ID of shareholder</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-7mpzn4-833\">ID information of shareholders owning more than 25% of shares</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-6oasqh-834\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-e8mt1o-835\">Proof of business</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-afncbm-836\">Documents to prove business activities, including:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-9viwlu-837\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-zn1k64-838\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7w-0um9l5-149\">Pictures of business office/headquarters</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-j3zuw2-839\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-glv59j-150\">Tax payment documents (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-f7uffa-840\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-5jj3wj-151\">Import invoices proving the origin of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-ov4vbs-841\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-9z0ok3-152\">Warehouse images, distribution agency contracts (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-wlxe4t-842\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-1oi6ti-153\">Sales invoices</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-jao5j4-843\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-ybg8xk-154\">Image of the sales system recording online transactions (buyer information</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-861cit-844\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-6oo13y-155\">quantity of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-fi3tqq-845\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-j7rpal-156\">Value of goods</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-5mfgvy-846\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-zb4rkn-157\">Shipping bill corresponding to the transaction</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-apgijo-847\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-v5o1bt-848\">Website/App Certificate</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykw-u3mgi6-849\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-b78irm-850\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-k4i4ss-158\">Website registration certificate</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-p7k527-851\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7x-pqy1pp-159\">Google Play or App Store account certificate</p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-5ap3lg-852\"><a id=\"_3xr9q1dsrh6z\" display=\"false\"></a>KYC documents for Reseller/Distributor</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-cicfjt-853\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-434k8o-854\">Documents</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-7lgo1j-855\">Details</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-sm94pu-856\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-vubbrc-857\">Business License</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-9e8szb-858\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-1l2h6e-859\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7y-z2bij5-160\">Business file</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuykx-uw5jgw-860\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7y-cjv84m-161\">Certificate of incorporation</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-c0xepw-861\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-fvkfgz-862\">Sub-license for specific industry (if applicable)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-ahdyvk-863\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-rldqos-864\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7y-me2dp9-162\">Only for the Payment service providers/money service operators/remittance Merchants (Reseller/remittance merchant): require PAYMENT SERVICE PROVIDERS/MONEY SERVICE OPERATORS/REMITTANCE LICENSE</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-4jsv79-865\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-witwbq-866\">Passport of legal representative</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-vcze6o-867\"><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-ycfiqb-868\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7z-ljb616-163\">The passport should not be expired</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-jm3ktj-869\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r7z-hi1uv3-164\">The passport should show the full picture of the representative</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-mscr1n-870\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyky-t6sn4g-871\">Ownership structure chart</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-vwvjlo-872\">Chart that shows the ownership and shareholder of the company</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-7dhefi-873\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-6fa23x-874\">Memorandum and Article of Association</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-ab8zj1-875\">Memorandum and Article of Association (for  MSB / Remittance)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-vjyztc-876\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-1bocsu-877\">Beneficial owner information</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuykz-nzfw7u-878\">Individuals and organizations owning more than 25% of capital or shares in the company</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-ugnrnx-879\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-e3mwdd-880\">ID of shareholder</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-oxuzr7-881\">ID information of shareholders owning more than 25% of shares</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\" style=\"\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-va0d14-882\">8</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-4d8c0o-883\">AML Policy</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r80-bhx45i-165\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mlhiuyl0-rlplu1-884\"><a id=\"_leai602f6gye\" display=\"false\"></a></h2><p data-block-id=\"mmka2r80-pr9eoi-166\"></p>","ContentType":2},{"Code":"id","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"th","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"es-mx","Content":null,"ContentType":2}]